<node id="Yushan Bank">
  <data key="d0">Yushan Bank</data>
  <data key="d1">customer</data>
  <data key="d2">Yushan Bank is a financial institution that has been identified as the customer for whom various maintenance records are created and processed. These records indicate Yushan Bank's association with maintenance activities, suggesting ongoing interactions or services related to its operations. The repeated mentions of Yushan Bank in this context highlight its consistent role as a key client involved in maintenance processes. Specifically, Yushan Bank is the customer for whom maintenance records are created and being created, underscoring its continuous engagement with these services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23ee3da56ce07c9d486440fd8828fb66&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d4b8d6a4083193dd527549b98f74032&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9f7e790874cf9a3bf3593da7426be961&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-317cd3b1caf5869b2eae3938639d1dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20bb4161f0377445984f317c8c8de2e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-675f8c7c35ccf6eca14c59f112de7e29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33c836c57335d57c5dc66e8610bb0491&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-34b4aa4a40e13df4259f0278f9dc808b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ea7c1467675e2cfba39da931edc603b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fc9a0f7f04d2836444cfc3f58954af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28867d6c4625c440944590b513e76618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fd1383fcca67c9836aaadab403cfc49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-722c5c3a89e4a11e2005fe2113628014&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15e9a08292af39fc0496ff95f463226e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32a3c902d9f460321eeafc73be30071b</data>
