<node id="Maintenance Record">
  <data key="d0">Maintenance Record</data>
  <data key="d1">record</data>
  <data key="d2">The Maintenance Record is a comprehensive document that outlines various maintenance tasks and activities performed across different systems and organizations. It provides detailed information about specific actions taken during particular time frames to address issues or perform upgrades.

For Yushan Bank, the Maintenance Record details several significant maintenance activities. One entry documents actions taken to resolve an issue with their vCenter system. Another records a maintenance task performed on the NetApp F8200 server. Additionally, there is documentation of an upgrade to the Splunk version for Yushan Bank's credit card processing system. The record also includes details about maintenance activities performed on Firemon equipment and the Splunk service and data confirmation before a server room move for Yushan Securities.

The Maintenance Record covers tasks performed by specific individuals. For instance, James Li conducted a maintenance activity on 2025/03/15 from 13:00 to 14:00. Leon Lee is noted for performing a maintenance task for Taiwan Bank. Ben Jen carried out a maintenance task on 2025/12/22 from 11:00 to 11:30 for Kai Chi Man Life. Additionally, the record documents activities performed by Brian Wang on July 9, 2025, and John Lee on March 21, 2025, who handled a Splunk SH issue.

The Maintenance Record also includes details about activities and actions taken during the maintenance process for various entities, including Kai Jie Life, Kai Ji Ren Shu, and 南山人壽's system. For example, it documents the details of the service provided to Kai Ji Ren Shu, including the actions taken and the time frame on 2025/05/08 from 10:00 to 11:30. Additionally, it details the maintenance activities performed on the Financial Building 6F printer system.

The Maintenance Record documents specific tasks such as an onsite operation performed by Linda Hsu at Taiwan Bank and maintenance work conducted on 2025/02/26 from 16:00 to 21:20. These entries ensure that all relevant information is documented, providing a clear record of maintenance efforts across different entities and systems.

The Maintenance Record serves as an essential tool for tracking and managing maintenance activities, ensuring that all issues are addressed promptly and efficiently. It also documents the details of equipment setup and configuration tasks performed by Tim Chen and Jie Chen, as well as specific actions related to Splunk work items on July 29, 2025. Additionally, it includes information about maintenance tasks for Cathay Life and Kai Ji Ren Shu, including actions taken by Kimi Lee on May 28, 2025. The record also details the maintenance activities performed on a system or software and specific tasks conducted by Jerry Zhang for Yushan Bank.

The Maintenance Record documents various maintenance tasks performed at specific times, such as on 2025/10/28 from 14:01 to 18:30, on 2025/07/16 from 10:00 to 12:00, and during the upgrade of Testserverfarm. It also covers activities related to Cathay Bank's system on April 2, 2025, and the maintenance of Kai Jie Ren Shu's system.

Additionally, the Maintenance Record details specific actions taken for entities such as Kai Chi People Life Insurance, including system updates and standby procedures. For Kai Chi Man Life, it includes the addition of a new switch and service verification during a maintenance session. It also addresses vulnerabilities in the ESXi system and documents activities performed on Kai Jie Bank's systems, including adjustments to email forwarding and file transfer reports.

The Maintenance Record further details the Splunk ECS package update for Kai Jie Ren Shu, handled by Chuen Lin and John Lee on 2025/05/27 from 10:00 to 11:30. It also documents maintenance activities performed on 2025/06/18 from 15:00 to 18:00, involving multiple engineers and focusing on NSX testing projects.

The Maintenance Record covers specific maintenance activities for other entities such as Tai Xin Securities' system and details the actions taken during the upgrade of IntrAP-UAT-LTM. It documents the maintenance activities performed on February 12, 2025, and addresses a vulnerability in Cathay Bank's system. Additionally, it includes details about maintenance tasks performed on specific dates and times, such as on 2025/02/11 from 09:30 to 17:30.

The Maintenance Record is also used for documenting the activities and actions taken during the maintenance process for 玉山銀行. It details the actions and status of a maintenance task performed by Ct on June 4, 2025, and documents the details of a maintenance activity conducted by engineers Alex Ji and Lynn Yao at Taiwan Bank. Additionally, it includes information about the maintenance activities performed on Cathay Life's DB server farm and Kai Jie Ren Shu's system, including actions taken and status descriptions.

The Maintenance Record also documents specific details such as the maintenance activities performed on Kai Chi Man Life's systems and on October 30, 2025. It includes information about maintenance tasks conducted by Louis Chan for 玉山銀行 on 2025/04/18 from 11:00 to 17:00 and on 2025/05/23 from 15:00 to 18:30. Additionally, it covers a maintenance task performed on June 13, 2025, and details the actions and status of specific devices during maintenance activities.

The Maintenance Record also includes entries specifically detailing issues and actions taken for Nan Shan Life Insurance's Splunk backup problem and documents the actions taken during the maintenance process for Kai Chi People Life Insurance. Additionally, it details the activities and status of equipment inspections at Yushan Bank. The maintenance record also details the actions taken and the status of the issue with Cymulate for 南山人壽.

Additionally, the Maintenance Record documents the details of the maintenance activities performed on Kai Bank's system. It also includes specific entries documenting the maintenance activities conducted by Jack for Kai Jie Ren Shu.

The Maintenance Record also documents the details of the DDOS issue and the actions taken by Aleric. Furthermore, it addresses vulnerabilities in Yushan China's system. The Maintenance Record documents the details of the service provided to Kai Chi Man by Link. Additionally, the Maintenance Record documents the details of the maintenance activities performed on DMZ-UAT-LTM for Kgilife.

The Maintenance Record also documents a hardware failure and its resolution for Yushan China. It includes an entry detailing a specific maintenance task performed on 2025/05/29 from 10:00 to 12:00, though the details of this task are not specified in the provided descriptions. Additionally, it documents the details of the maintenance activity performed by Link on 2025/02/26 from 09:00 to 14:00.

The Maintenance Record also includes a specific entry documenting the maintenance task performed on Gigamon for Yushan Bank. It also documents the details of the maintenance work performed on 2025/02/17 from 14:30 to 17:30.

Additionally, the Maintenance Record documents the details of a maintenance task performed on 2025/07/22 from 10:00 to 17:00 by Jerry Fang and Yuki Jiang for Yamaha Bank. The Maintenance Record also includes an entry detailing activities and status of a maintenance task for Kai Chi Life.

The Maintenance Record documents the details of the maintenance activity performed by Jack on 2025/05/08 from 09:30 to 16:30. It also documents the details of the system anomaly and the actions taken to resolve it.

Additionally, the Maintenance Record details the upgrade process of ODA X8-2HA from version 19.18 to 19.22, including specific actions taken during the maintenance period.</data>
