<node id="玉山銀行">
  <data key="d0">玉山銀行</data>
  <data key="d1">customer</data>
  <data key="d2">玉山銀行, also known as Yushan Bank in English, is consistently identified as a customer associated with various maintenance records. The descriptions uniformly indicate that 玉山銀行 is the entity for whom these maintenance records are created and maintained. There is no conflicting information regarding the identity or role of Yushan Bank in this context; all provided descriptions align in stating that 玉山銀行 is a customer involved in maintenance services.

The repeated mentions across different descriptions reinforce the consistency of Yushan Bank's role as a customer associated with maintenance records. This uniformity suggests a clear and unambiguous relationship between Yushan Bank and the maintenance services it utilizes. The bank is explicitly noted as the customer for whom maintenance activities are being recorded, processed, and maintained.

There is one instance where the name "Yuanshan Bank" appears instead of "Yushan Bank." However, given the context and the consistency in the descriptions, it is likely a typographical error rather than a reference to a different entity. Therefore, all references can be attributed to 玉山銀行 (Yushan Bank).&lt;SEP&gt;Yushan Bank is the customer for whom the maintenance record is created.</data>
