<node id="Brian Wang">
  <data key="d0">Brian Wang</data>
  <data key="d1">engineer</data>
  <data key="d2">Brian Wang is an engineer known for his involvement in various maintenance tasks. He has handled maintenance records and tasks for several financial institutions, including Yushan Securities, Taiwan Bank, and Cathay Bank. His role typically involves managing maintenance tasks, ensuring that these institutions' systems and equipment are well-maintained and operational.&lt;SEP&gt;Brian Wang is an engineer involved in the maintenance of the system.</data>
