  <data key="d1">engineer</data>
  <data key="d2">Kimi Lee is an engineer who has been involved in various maintenance activities across different systems and organizations. Notably, Kimi Lee has handled the maintenance of Kai Jie Life, which appears to be a system or service related to life insurance or similar services. Additionally, Kimi Lee has been instrumental in managing the maintenance records for Kai Ji Ren Shu, indicating a significant role in ensuring the upkeep and operational efficiency of this entity.

Kimi Lee's responsibilities also extend to handling maintenance activities for Kai Chi People Life Insurance, suggesting a broad expertise in maintaining systems related to life insurance. This involvement highlights Kimi Lee's versatility and proficiency in managing different types of maintenance tasks within the insurance sector.

Beyond these specific roles, Kimi Lee has also been involved in the maintenance of more general systems such as printer systems and DB server farms. These activities demonstrate Kimi Lee's technical skills and ability to manage a variety of technological infrastructures, ensuring their smooth operation and reliability.&lt;SEP&gt;Kimi Lee is the engineer who handled the maintenance record for Kai Jie Ren Shu.&lt;SEP&gt;Kimi Lee is an engineer involved in the maintenance record for Kai Ji Ren Shu.&lt;SEP&gt;Kimi Lee is an engineer involved in the maintenance of Kai Jie Ren Shu's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Kimi Lee is an engineer involved in the maintenance of a system.&lt;SEP&gt;Kimi Lee is an engineer involved in the maintenance record for Kai Ji Ren Shu.</data>
