  <data key="d2">Jack is an engineer who has been extensively involved in various maintenance activities and records for several organizations. Notably, Jack handled the maintenance for Kai Ji Ren Shu, which includes both the maintenance activities and the maintenance record. This involvement encompasses managing the maintenance tasks and systems associated with Kai Ji Ren Shu.

In addition to his work with Kai Ji Ren Shu, Jack has been involved in the maintenance of a printer system and a DB server farm. His responsibilities also extend to other entities such as Cathay Life, where he managed the maintenance record. Furthermore, Jack has been associated with the maintenance records for Kai Chi People Life Insurance and Kai Chi Man Life.

There is some ambiguity regarding the exact nature of his involvement with Kai Jie Life, but it is clear that Jack plays a significant role in the maintenance activities for multiple organizations. His duties often involve handling maintenance tasks and records, demonstrating his versatility and expertise in engineering and maintenance across different systems and entities.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is the engineer who handled the maintenance record for Kai Chi Life.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is an engineer who handled the maintenance issue for Kai Chi Life.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is an engineer involved in the maintenance record for Kai Ji Ren Shu.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is an engineer involved in the maintenance of a system.</data>
