<node id="Annie Chang">
  <data key="d0">Annie Chang</data>
  <data key="d1">engineer</data>
  <data key="d2">Annie Chang is an engineer known for her involvement in various maintenance activities. She has been notably associated with the maintenance of several entities, including Kai Ji Ren Shu and Kai Jie Ren Shu. On June 19, 2025, she specifically handled the maintenance of Kai Ji Ren Shu's system.

Additionally, Annie Chang has been involved in handling the maintenance activities for Kai Chi Ren Shu, which appears to be a variant or related entity to Kai Ji Ren Shu. Her responsibilities also extend to managing the maintenance records for Kai Chi People Life Insurance and performing maintenance tasks for Kai Chi Man Life. These roles highlight her expertise in system maintenance and her ability to handle complex engineering tasks across different platforms.

Annie Chang's work demonstrates her versatility as an engineer, capable of managing various systems and ensuring their smooth operation through meticulous maintenance activities.</data>
