<node id="John Lee">
  <data key="d0">John Lee</data>
  <data key="d1">engineer</data>
  <data key="d2">John Lee is an engineer known for his involvement in various maintenance tasks across different organizations. He has been particularly active in handling the maintenance records and systems for several financial institutions.

Lee's responsibilities include managing the maintenance record for Nan Shan Life Insurance, a prominent life insurance company. His role involves ensuring that all systems are properly maintained to support the company's operations. Additionally, he is involved in the maintenance of Kai Jie Bank's systems, indicating his expertise in handling complex financial systems. Lee has also been associated with Taiwan Bank and Kai Jie Ren Shu, where he has handled similar maintenance tasks.

Overall, John Lee's work spans multiple organizations, demonstrating his versatility and proficiency in system maintenance within the financial sector. His contributions are crucial for ensuring the smooth operation of these institutions' technological infrastructure.&lt;SEP&gt;John Lee is the engineer handling the maintenance tasks for Taiwan Bank.</data>
