  <data key="d1">engineer</data>
  <data key="d2">Crystal Shen is an engineer known for her involvement in the maintenance of various financial institutions' systems. She has handled maintenance tasks for several prominent organizations, including Nan Shan Life Insurance and Cathay Bank. Specifically, Crystal Shen has been responsible for maintaining the systems at Nan Shan Life Insurance, which is also referred to as 南山人壽. Additionally, she has managed the maintenance records for Cathay Bank, ensuring that their systems remain operational and secure.

Crystal Shen's expertise extends beyond these institutions; she has also been involved in the maintenance of Kai Jie Bank's systems. Furthermore, her responsibilities include handling maintenance tasks for Cathay Life, demonstrating her versatility and proficiency in managing diverse technological needs within the financial sector.</data>
