<edge source="World Athletics Federation" target="Noah Carter">
  <data key="d7">138.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Noah Carter and the World Athletics Federation have a significant relationship centered around the validation of an exceptional athletic achievement. The World Athletics Federation has officially recognized and endorsed Noah Carter's performance by validating his new 100-meter (100m) sprint record. This record was set during a championship event, underscoring its significance in competitive athletics.

The consistent validation by the World Athletics Federation emphasizes the official recognition of Noah Carter's achievement within the sport. The federation's endorsement solidifies Noah Carter's performance as a notable milestone in athletic history. The World Athletics Federation oversees the championship where Noah Carter set this new record, further highlighting the importance of his accomplishment.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's record-breaking achievement.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.</data>
