<edge source="Yushan Bank" target="Maintenance Record">
  <data key="d7">12.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Maintenance Record pertains to Yushan Bank and details various aspects of maintenance activities performed on their behalf. The record specifically outlines the actions taken during a specific time frame to address an issue with their vCenter. It is associated with Yushan Bank as the customer undergoing these maintenance activities, which were performed by Louis Chan. The Maintenance Record encompasses all the maintenance activities carried out for Yushan Bank, ensuring that the bank's systems and infrastructure are properly maintained and operational.&lt;SEP&gt;Yushan Bank is associated with the maintenance record that documents the activities performed on 2025/04/18 from 11:00 to 17:00.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record pertains to the services provided to Yushan Bank.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record pertains to the activities performed on Yushan Bank's system.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record pertains to Yushan Bank and documents the details of the maintenance work performed.</data>
  <data key="d9">customer,customer involvement,customer maintenance,customer relationship,maintenance,maintenance activities,maintenance documentation,maintenance record,maintenance task,record documentation,service,system maintenance</data>
