<edge source="Maintenance Record" target="Jack">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Jack, in relation to Maintenance Record, plays a crucial role in documenting and managing various maintenance activities across different entities. His responsibilities are integral to ensuring that all maintenance activities are properly documented and managed, contributing to the overall efficiency and reliability of the systems within these organizations.

Jack's involvement extends to multiple organizations. He is documented as one of the engineers involved in the maintenance record for Cathay Life's DB server farm. Additionally, he handles the maintenance records for Kai Chi Man Life, Kai Ji Ren Shu, and Kai Chi People Life Insurance. This comprehensive involvement showcases his role as an engineer responsible for documenting maintenance actions taken during sessions for these entities.

Jack's responsibilities are not limited to a single organization; he is also one of the engineers handling the maintenance record for Kai Chi Man Life. His role includes documenting the maintenance activities for Kai Jie Life, indicating a direct responsibility for recording these actions. Similarly, he handles the maintenance recorded in the document, suggesting an active role in maintaining and updating records.

The Maintenance Record documents the activities performed by Jack, highlighting his active involvement in managing and updating these records. This documentation is crucial for ensuring that all maintenance activities are properly tracked and managed, contributing to the overall efficiency and reliability of the systems within these organizations.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack handled the maintenance record for Kai Chi Life on 2025/05/08 from 09:30 to 16:30.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is documented as an engineer involved in the maintenance record for Kai Ji Ren Shu.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is involved in the maintenance record documenting the upgrade of Taoyuan Cp1570.</data>
