<edge source="Maintenance Record" target="玉山銀行">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Yushan Bank, also known as 玉山銀行 in Chinese, is a financial institution that has an association with a Maintenance Record. This record details the work performed on their systems and documents various maintenance activities. The Maintenance Record provides comprehensive information about the actions taken during these tasks and updates on their status.

The Maintenance Record is specifically created for Yushan Bank to document all maintenance activities related to their equipment. It includes detailed records of issues such as a DDOS attack, along with the actions taken by entities like Aleric to address these problems. The record also highlights specific instances where maintenance was handled by individuals such as Ben Chang on particular dates and times, for example, on 2025/01/10 from 10:00 to 11:00.

Yushan Bank is identified as the customer associated with this Maintenance Record. The record serves as a crucial tool for tracking all maintenance-related activities, ensuring that Yushan Bank's systems and equipment are well-maintained and operational.&lt;SEP&gt;Yushan Bank is the customer for whom the maintenance record was created and documented.</data>
  <data key="d9">customer,customer activity,customer involvement,documentation,maintenance,maintenance documentation,record association</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-8d5b145e19b4a1cb13aa16a167aae29e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3aa0ab2663b0b34973e16ecd941a7ae0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-061b23539a233aa091e0df376b7434a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62fb7b422e9feb0e7c7f098618ff81dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dedabd2a99aa8c5502f9b5efac0f752e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c73f4e0a3cdf13117a3a72c62a880ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c1df4d46176c98a1b513c16f11b1fc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e74343ae1e54bbd1692b8eaee0d1b54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7cc7c5a957ff8c75ee5351de090f532</data>
